title: GameCube Ads Were Kinda Weird
description:
Nintendo GameCube was a box. A Cube. A Square in 3D. Mario was there sometimes. Sometimes he wasn’t. What fun.

You had a Metroid or two, some Donkey Kong, and the occasional Luigi. And they had TV ads. So I’m gonna talk about them.
